## Hardware

### Target Board
Waveshare ESP32-S3-Touch-LCD-1.47

### Sensor Wiring
| Sensor | Pin | ESP32-S3 GPIO |
|---|---|---|
| BMV080 | VCC | 3.3V |
| BMV080 | GND | GND |
| BMV080 | SDA | GPIO6 |
| BMV080 | SCL | GPIO5 |
| ENS160 | VCC | 3.3V (shared with BMV080) |
| ENS160 | GND | GND |
| ENS160 | SDA | GPIO6 (shared with BMV080) |
| ENS160 | SCL | GPIO5 (shared with BMV080) |
| GPS | VCC | VBUS (5V) |
| GPS | GND | GND |
| GPS | TX | GPIO8 |
| GPS | RX | GPIO7 |

> ⚠️ BMV080 is sensitive to power supply noise. Add a 10µF and 100nF ceramic capacitor across VCC and GND as close to the sensor as possible.

> ⚠️ GPS must be powered from VBUS (5V), not 3.3V. Keep GPS on a separate power rail from the BMV080 to avoid supply noise.
